Jennie Kwan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennie_Kwan 0 Jennie Kwan (born Jennifer Trinidad Fernando; September 9, 1973) is an American actress and singer. She is known for her roles as Samantha "Sam" Woo on California Dreams and as the voice of Suki on Avatar: The Last Airbender.
